Class AbstractVoidVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • kodkod.ast.visitor.AbstractVoidVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VoidVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractVoidVisitor
extends Object
implements VoidVisitor
    Implements a depth first traversal of the kodkod AST.
